name: 🎁 naughty or nice?
description:
if you were naughty, you get the purple gift. It's shaking a little and there's some kind of scratching sounds coming out of it. what could it be?

if you were nice, you get the pink gift. It feels very light when you pick it up, almost as if it was empty, but the gift bearer told you the contents were very precious. what could it be?

merry xmas 2021⭐
